A northern suburb of Peterborough , Cambridgeshire ( OS grid ref TF1702 ) . A suburb of the City of Liverpool , Merseyside ( OS grid ref SJ3694 ) . A hamlet in Eccleshall parish, Stafford borough , Staffordshire ( OS grid ref SJ8527 ) . A suburban area in Stone parish, Stafford borough , Staffordshire ( OS grid ref SJ9033 ) . A village and civil parish in the City of Wakefield , West Yorkshire ( OS grid ref SE3517 ) .
A settlement in Waikato , New Zealand .
